sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as Setup
    participant Mac as MacSetup
    participant Linux as LinuxSetup
    participant Config as ConfigManager
    participant Docker as DockerManager
    participant PHP as PhpManager
    participant Caddy as CaddyManager

    User->>CLI: orbit setup --tld=ccc
    CLI->>CLI: parse and normalize options
    
    alt Darwin
        CLI->>Mac: run with options
        Mac->>PHP: install PHP versions
        Mac->>Caddy: configure Caddy
        Mac->>Docker: setup Docker services
        Mac-->>CLI: success or failure
    else Linux
        CLI->>Linux: run with options
        Linux->>PHP: install PHP versions
        Linux->>Caddy: configure Caddy
        Linux->>Docker: setup Docker services
        Linux-->>CLI: success or failure
    end

    CLI-->>User: result
